                <p rend="flushleft">I <hi rend="italic">Agenda</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council adopted the following agenda for this meeting: <list>
                        <label>1</label>
                        <item>Peace Conference (draft invitation and rules of procedure)</item>
                        <label>2</label>
                        <item>Reparation (final text)</item>
                        <label>3</label>
                        <item>German questions</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II <hi rend="italic">Peace Conference</hi> (Draft invitation and
                    rules of procedure)</p>
                <p>An exchange of views was held on this question.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting of the Council</hi>
                </p>
                <p>5 p.m. the same day</p>
